# ───────── Credentials / local config (safety net) ─────────
# The app stores its Claude sessionKey in ~/.config/ai-mon/config.json,
# which lives OUTSIDE this repository and is never committed. The patterns
# below are only a guard against accidentally adding a copy into the repo.
config.json
*.sessionkey
*.secret
secrets*
.env
.env.*

